Apache::Request::Redirect README File
=====================================

This module works under mod_perl and, given a client request
redirect it to another url.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   HTTP::Request
   HTTP::Response
   HTTP::Headers
   LWP::UserAgent
   URI

